nodes.text: Jat Kaa was a Lurmen male from the planet Mygeeto. Sometime during the war between the First Order and the Resistance, Kaa imported the beverages Coca-Cola, Diet Coke, Sprite, and Dasani to the Outer Rim world Batuu, where workers for his company, Jat Kaa's Coolers, sold them to travelers and locals at various locations throughout Black Spire Outpost.
